title: The second Head of State Election
description:
Cast your ballot using /vote. Choose only one option for the ballot, input using the character represent for that candidate. 
*Example:* ```
/vote a
```
https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/739002052809719909/1113990098934059008/image.png
footer: YOU DO NOT HAVE TO REVEAL YOUR BALLOT TO ANYBODY, INCLUDING GOVERNMENTAL OFFICERS!
